== Standard Upgrade vs Release Upgrade ==

This procedure is for normal ("everyday") upgrades of [[Qubes|{{q_project_name}}]] and will not perform a [[Release Upgrade]].

Before applying a release upgrade, it is recommended to first complete a standard upgrade in both the <code>{{whonix-gw}}</code> and <code>{{whonix-ws}}</code> Templates, via <code>xfce4-terminal</code>:

* <code>Qubes App Menu(blue/grey "Q")</code> &rarr; <code>Template: {{whonix-gw}}</code> &rarr; <code>xfce4-terminal</code>
* <code>Qubes App Menu(blue/grey "Q")</code> &rarr; <code>Template: {{whonix-ws}}</code> &rarr; <code>xfce4-terminal</code>

Afterward, perform the [[#Standard_Upgrade_Steps|Standard Upgrade Steps]] below in both terminals.

